# SnapRep API Design Documentation (v2.0)

> **Version**: v2.0 (Page-Based Architecture)
> **Date**: 2024-10-30
> **Architecture**: NestJS + Supabase Hybrid

---

## 📋 API Overview & Quick Reference

### Design Philosophy
- **Page-Centric Design**: APIs organized by frontend pages for clarity
- **Supabase First**: Leverage built-in features (Auth, RLS, Storage, Realtime)
- **Performance Priority**: TTV ≤30s, Card generation ≤800ms
- **Offline First**: Core features work offline, sync when online

---

## 🗺️ Complete API Map (一目了然)

### API Summary by Page

| Page | Feature | API Endpoint | Method | Supabase/NestJS |
|------|---------|-------------|--------|-----------------|
| **🏠 HomePage** | 获取场景列表 | `/rest/v1/scenarios` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 获取器材列表 | `/rest/v1/equipment` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 获取当前主题周 | `/api/v1/theme-weeks/current` | GET | NestJS |
| | 加入主题周 | `/api/v1/theme-weeks/{id}/join` | POST | NestJS |
| | AI 物体识别 | `/api/v1/ai/recognize-equipment` | POST | NestJS |
| **🎯 WorkoutGuidePage** | 获取意图选项 | N/A (前端hardcoded) | - | Frontend |
| | 获取场景选项 | `/rest/v1/scenarios` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 获取器材选项 | `/rest/v1/equipment` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| **🎪 WorkoutResultPage** | 快速推荐(60秒) | `/api/v1/recommendations/quick` | POST | NestJS |
| | 替换单个动作 | `/api/v1/recommendations/replace` | POST | NestJS |
| | 获取替换候选 | `/api/v1/recommendations/alternatives` | GET | NestJS |
| | 创建训练会话 | `/rest/v1/workout_sessions` | POST | Supabase Auto |
| | 更新会话状态 | `/rest/v1/workout_sessions/{id}` | PATCH | Supabase Auto |
| **🎨 ResultCardPage** | 生成分享卡片 | `/api/v1/cards/generate` | POST | NestJS |
| | 计算稀有度 | `/api/v1/rarity/calculate/{code}` | GET | NestJS |
| | 上传卡片图片 | `supabase.storage.upload()` | POST | Supabase Storage |
| | 保存卡片记录 | `/rest/v1/share_cards` | POST | Supabase Auto |
| **👤 MyPage - Cards** | 获取我的卡片 | `/rest/v1/share_cards` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 卡片详情 | `/rest/v1/share_cards/{id}` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 更新卡片 | `/rest/v1/share_cards/{id}` | PATCH | Supabase Auto |
| **👤 MyPage - History** | 获取训练历史 | `/rest/v1/workout_sessions` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 获取每日统计 | `/rest/v1/daily_trainings` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 月历视图 | `/api/v1/users/{id}/calendar` | GET | NestJS |
| **👤 MyPage - Settings** | 获取用户信息 | `/rest/v1/users/{id}` | GET | Supabase Auto |
| | 更新用户设置 | `/rest/v1/users/{id}` | PATCH | Supabase Auto |
| | 匿名登录 | `supabase.auth.signInAnonymously()` | - | Supabase Auth |
| | 邮箱登录 | `supabase.auth.signInWithOtp()` | - | Supabase Auth |

### API Count Summary
- **Supabase Auto REST API**: 12 endpoints (基础 CRUD)
- **Supabase Auth**: 2 flows (认证授权)
- **Supabase Storage**: 1 bucket (媒体文件)
- **NestJS Custom API**: 7 endpoints (复杂业务逻辑)
- **Total**: ~22 API endpoints

---

## 🏠 HomePage APIs

### Page Overview
- **Page Goal**: 快速激活用户开始训练，展示多个进入方式
- **Key Features**: Hero CTA, 场景快选, 器材选择, 主题周, AI识别
- **Performance Target**: 首屏加载 ≤2秒

---

### 1.1 Get Scenarios List (获取场景列表)

**用途**: 首页场景区显示「办公室」「客厅/沙发」等场景选项

```typescript
GET /rest/v1/scenarios?select=*&is_active=eq.true&order=display_order
```

**Implementation**: Supabase Auto REST API

**Request**: 无需 body

**Response**:
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "scenario-001",
      "code": "office",
      "name": "Office",
      "description": "Perfect for desk breaks",
      "isActive": true,
      "displayOrder": 1,
      "defaultEquipment": ["chair", "wall"],  // 预设器材
      "noiseLevel": "QUIET",
      "spaceRequired": "SMALL"
    },
    {
      "id": "scenario-002",
      "code": "living_room",
      "name": "Living Room",
      "description": "Relax on your couch",
      "isActive": true,
      "displayOrder": 2,
      "defaultEquipment": ["sofa", "chair"],
      "noiseLevel": "NORMAL",
      "spaceRequired": "MEDIUM"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Frontend Usage**:
```dart
// Flutter code
final scenarios = await supabase
  .from('scenarios')
  .select('*')
  .eq('is_active', true)
  .order('display_order');

// 渲染场景 Chips
scenarios.forEach((scenario) {
  ScenarioChip(
    label: scenario['name'],
    onTap: () => navigateToResultPage(
      equipment: scenario['default_equipment']
    )
  )
});
```

**Caching Strategy**:
- TTL: 1 day (场景不常变)
- Storage: Local SharedPreferences

---

### 1.2 Get Equipment List (获取器材列表)

**用途**: 首页物品区显示「椅子」「墙面」「水瓶」等器材选项

```typescript
GET /rest/v1/equipment?select=*&is_active=eq.true&order=display_order
```

**Implementation**: Supabase Auto REST API

**Request**: 无需 body

**Response**:
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "eq-001",
      "code": "chair",
      "name": "Chair",
      "category": "FURNITURE",
      "iconUrl": "https://storage.supabase.co/icons/chair.svg",
      "isActive": true,
      "displayOrder": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "eq-002",
      "code": "wall",
      "name": "Wall",
      "category": "WALL",
      "iconUrl": "https://storage.supabase.co/icons/wall.svg",
      "isActive": true,
      "displayOrder": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "eq-003",
      "code": "hands_free",
      "name": "No Equipment",
      "category": "BODYWEIGHT",
      "iconUrl": "https://storage.supabase.co/icons/hands-free.svg",
      "isActive": true,
      "displayOrder": 1
    }
  ]
}
```

**Frontend Usage**:
```dart
// 渲染器材 Grid
GridView.builder(
  itemCount: equipment.length,
  itemBuilder: (ctx, i) => EquipmentTile(
    icon: equipment[i]['icon_url'],
    label: equipment[i]['name'],
    onTap: () => navigateToGuidePage(
      preselectedEquipment: equipment[i]['code']
    )
  )
);
```

**Caching Strategy**:
- TTL: 1 day
- Storage: Local Database

