### 1.3 Get Current Theme Week (获取当前主题周)

**用途**: 首页主题周区显示「本周:#椅子日」及奖励信息

```typescript
GET /api/v1/theme-weeks/current
```

**Implementation**: NestJS Custom API

**Why NestJS**: 需要计算用户参与状态、全局统计、剩余时间等复杂逻辑

**Request**:
- Headers: `Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>`

**Response**:
```json
{
  "current": {
    "id": "theme-001",
    "code": "chair_week_2024_44",
    "title": "Chair Week",
    "description": "Complete 3 chair exercises to unlock exclusive sticker skin",
    "equipmentCode": "chair",
    "startDate": "2024-10-28",
    "endDate": "2024-11-03",
    "targetExerciseCount": 3,
    "reward": {
      "type": "skin",
      "data": {
        "skinName": "Chair Master",
        "rarityBoost": 0.1
      }
    },
    "participation": {
      "isJoined": true,          // 用户是否已加入
      "progress": {
        "completed": 2,           // 已完成动作数
        "target": 3,              // 目标动作数
        "percentage": 66.7
      },
      "timeLeft": "2 days 14 hours"  // 剩余时间
    },
    "globalStats": {
      "totalParticipants": 12567,     // 全球参与人数
      "completionRate": 78.3          // 完成率
    }
  },
  "upcoming": [
    {
      "title": "Bottle Week",
      "equipmentCode": "bottle",
      "startDate": "2024-11-04"
    },
    {
      "title": "Backpack Week",
      "equipmentCode": "backpack",
      "startDate": "2024-11-11"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Frontend Usage**:
```dart
// 主题周卡片
ThemeWeekCard(
  title: themeWeek['title'],
  description: themeWeek['description'],
  progress: themeWeek['participation']['progress'],
  onJoinTap: () => joinThemeWeek(themeWeek['id']),
  onStartTap: () => navigateToResultPage(
    equipment: [themeWeek['equipment_code']],
    themeWeekId: themeWeek['id']
  )
);
```

**Error Handling**:
```json
// 无主题周时
{
  "current": null,
  "upcoming": [],
  "message": "No active theme week at the moment"
}
```

