### 1.4 Join Theme Week (加入主题周)

**用途**: 用户点击「一键加入」按钮后调用

```typescript
POST /api/v1/theme-weeks/{themeWeekId}/join
```

**Implementation**: NestJS Custom API

**Why NestJS**: 需要创建参与记录、验证用户状态、防止重复加入

**Request**:
```json
{
  "userId": "user-123"  // 从 JWT token 自动提取
}
```

**Response**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "participation": {
    "id": "participation-456",
    "themeWeekId": "theme-001",
    "userId": "user-123",
    "status": "JOINED",
    "joinedAt": "2024-10-30T10:30:00Z",
    "completedCount": 0,
    "targetCount": 3,
    "isCompleted": false
  },
  "message": "Successfully joined Chair Week challenge!"
}
```

**Frontend Usage**:
```dart
// 加入按钮点击
onJoinPressed() async {
  final result = await apiService.joinThemeWeek(themeWeekId);
  if (result['success']) {
    showSnackBar('Successfully joined!');
    navigateToResultPage(equipment: ['chair']);
  }
}
```

**Error Cases**:
```json
// 已加入
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "code": "ALREADY_JOINED",
    "message": "You have already joined this theme week"
  }
}

// 主题周已结束
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "code": "THEME_WEEK_ENDED",
    "message": "This theme week has ended"
  }
}
```

---

### 1.5 AI Equipment Recognition (AI 物体识别)

**用途**: 用户点击「拍照」图标后，上传图片识别器材

```typescript
POST /api/v1/ai/recognize-equipment
```

**Implementation**: NestJS + TensorFlow

**Why NestJS**: 需要运行 TensorFlow Lite 模型推理

**Request**: `multipart/form-data`
```typescript
{
  image: File,               // 图片文件
  confidence: 0.85,         // 可选: 置信度阈值 (default: 0.85)
  maxResults: 5             // 可选: 最大返回数量 (default: 5)
}
```

**Response**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "recognized": [
    {
      "equipmentCode": "chair",
      "confidence": 0.92,
      "boundingBox": {
        "x": 100,
        "y": 150,
        "width": 200,
        "height": 300
      },
      "equipmentInfo": {
        "id": "eq-001",
        "name": "Chair",
        "category": "FURNITURE",
        "iconUrl": "https://storage.supabase.co/icons/chair.svg"
      }
    },
    {
      "equipmentCode": "wall",
      "confidence": 0.88,
      "boundingBox": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 100,
        "height": 400
      },
      "equipmentInfo": {
        "id": "eq-002",
        "name": "Wall",
        "category": "WALL",
        "iconUrl": "https://storage.supabase.co/icons/wall.svg"
      }
    }
  ],
  "fallbackSuggestions": [
    // 低置信度时的手动选择建议
    {
      "equipmentCode": "sofa",
      "name": "Sofa",
      "reason": "Similar to detected object"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Frontend Usage**:
```dart
// 拍照识别流程
onCameraPressed() async {
  final image = await ImagePicker().pickImage(source: ImageSource.camera);
  if (image == null) return;

  showLoading('Recognizing...');
  final result = await apiService.recognizeEquipment(image);
  hideLoading();

  if (result['recognized'].isNotEmpty) {
    // 高置信度: 自动预选
    if (result['recognized'][0]['confidence'] > 0.85) {
      navigateToGuidePage(
        preselectedEquipment: result['recognized'][0]['equipment_code']
      );
    } else {
      // 低置信度: 显示候选列表
      showEquipmentSuggestions(result['fallback_suggestions']);
    }
  }
}
```

**Performance Target**:
- Response time: <2s
- Model: TensorFlow Lite (mobile-optimized)
- Image preprocessing: Resize to 224×224

