## 🎯 WorkoutGuidePage APIs

### Page Overview
- **Page Goal**: 通过3步引导精准捕捉用户需求
- **Key Features**: 意图选择, 场景+器材选择, 部位选择
- **Performance Target**: 完成引导率 ≥80%

**Note**: 大部分引导选项为前端 hardcoded，复用 HomePage 的场景和器材 API

---

### 2.1 Get Intent Options (获取意图选项)

**Implementation**: Frontend Hardcoded

**Why**: 意图选项固定，无需后端 API

**Options**:
```dart
// lib/constants/workout_intents.dart
enum WorkoutIntent {
  RELAX,           // 放松 - 降紧张
  STRETCH,         // 舒展筋骨 - 拉伸活动度
  LIGHT_CARDIO,    // 适当运动 - 轻汗微心率
  STRENGTH         // 主体锻炼 - 轻力量稳定
}

final intentOptions = [
  IntentOption(
    intent: WorkoutIntent.RELAX,
    title: 'Relax',
    subtitle: 'Reduce tension',
    icon: '🧘'
  ),
  IntentOption(
    intent: WorkoutIntent.STRETCH,
    title: 'Stretch',
    subtitle: 'Improve flexibility',
    icon: '🤸'
  ),
  IntentOption(
    intent: WorkoutIntent.LIGHT_CARDIO,
    title: 'Light Exercise',
    subtitle: 'Light sweat, mild cardio',
    icon: '🏃'
  ),
  IntentOption(
    intent: WorkoutIntent.STRENGTH,
    title: 'Strength',
    subtitle: 'Light resistance, stability',
    icon: '💪'
  )
];
```

---

### 2.2 Get Scenarios & Equipment (获取场景和器材)

**Reuse**: HomePage APIs
- Scenarios: `GET /rest/v1/scenarios`
- Equipment: `GET /rest/v1/equipment`

**Additional Logic**: 场景切换时更新器材建议
```dart
// 场景切换逻辑 (前端)
onScenarioChanged(String scenarioCode) {
  final scenario = scenarios.firstWhere((s) => s['code'] == scenarioCode);
  final suggestedEquipment = scenario['default_equipment'];

  setState(() {
    // 自动更新器材预选
    selectedEquipment = suggestedEquipment;
  });
}
```

---

### 2.3 Get Target Muscles (获取目标部位)

**Implementation**: Frontend Hardcoded

**Options**:
```dart
// lib/constants/target_muscles.dart
enum TargetMuscle {
  FULL_BODY,      // 全身
  NECK_SHOULDER,  // 颈肩
  CHEST_BACK,     // 胸背
  CORE,           // 核心
  LEGS,           // 大腿
  GLUTES,         // 臀部
  CALVES,         // 小腿
  ARMS            // 手臂
}

final muscleOptions = [
  MuscleOption(muscle: TargetMuscle.FULL_BODY, label: 'Full Body', icon: '🧍'),
  MuscleOption(muscle: TargetMuscle.NECK_SHOULDER, label: 'Neck & Shoulders', icon: '🫱'),
  MuscleOption(muscle: TargetMuscle.CHEST_BACK, label: 'Chest & Back', icon: '🫁'),
  // ... 其他部位
];
```

