    );
  }
}
```

**Performance Optimization**:
- Image generation: Use Sharp (faster than Canvas for Node.js)
- Template pre-loading: Cache templates in memory
- Parallel processing: Generate multiple sizes concurrently
- CDN: Serve generated cards via Supabase CDN

