### 5.9 Authentication APIs (认证)

**Implementation**: Supabase Auth (无需自定义 API)

#### 匿名登录
```dart
// 匿名登录
final response = await supabase.auth.signInAnonymously();
if (response.user != null) {
  print('Signed in anonymously: ${response.user!.id}');
}
```

#### 邮箱登录 (Magic Link)
```dart
// 发送 Magic Link
await supabase.auth.signInWithOtp(
  email: 'user@example.com',
  emailRedirectTo: 'snaprep://login-callback'
);

// 用户点击邮件链接后自动登录
```

#### OAuth 登录
```dart
// Google 登录
await supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth(
  Provider.google,
  redirectTo: 'snaprep://login-callback'
);

// Apple 登录
await supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth(
  Provider.apple,
  redirectTo: 'snaprep://login-callback'
);
```

#### 登出
```dart
await supabase.auth.signOut();
```

---

## 🔐 Authentication & Authorization

### Supabase Auth Flow

```
1. 匿名用户 → supabase.auth.signInAnonymously()
   ↓
2. (可选) 绑定邮箱 → supabase.auth.signInWithOtp(email)
   ↓
3. (可选) OAuth 登录 → supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth(provider)
```

### RLS (Row Level Security) Policies

```sql
-- 用户只能访问自己的数据
CREATE POLICY "Users own data access" ON workout_sessions
FOR ALL TO authenticated
USING (user_id = auth.uid());

CREATE POLICY "Users own cards" ON share_cards
FOR ALL TO authenticated
USING (user_id = auth.uid());

-- 公开数据可被所有人访问
CREATE POLICY "Public scenarios readable" ON scenarios
FOR SELECT TO anon, authenticated
USING (is_active = true);

CREATE POLICY "Public equipment readable" ON equipment
FOR SELECT TO anon, authenticated
USING (is_active = true);

-- 分享卡片的访问控制
CREATE POLICY "Public cards viewable" ON share_cards
FOR SELECT TO anon, authenticated
USING (is_public = true OR user_id = auth.uid());
```

### JWT Token Usage

```dart
// 所有 Supabase 请求自动携带 JWT
final response = await supabase
  .from('workout_sessions')
  .select('*')
  .eq('user_id', userId);  // RLS 自动验证 userId = auth.uid()

// NestJS API 需要手动传递
final response = await http.post(
  Uri.parse('$apiUrl/api/v1/recommendations/quick'),
  headers: {
    'Authorization': 'Bearer ${supabase.auth.currentSession?.accessToken}',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
  },
  body: jsonEncode({...})
);
```

---

## ⚡ Performance & Optimization

### Caching Strategy

```typescript
// Redis 缓存策略
- Equipment list: TTL 1 day
- Scenario list: TTL 1 day
- Exercise library: TTL 1 hour
- User preferences: TTL 10 minutes
- Rarity rankings: TTL 1 hour
- Theme week info: TTL 6 hours
```

### Database Indexes

```sql
-- 关键索引
CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY idx_exercises_recommendation
ON exercises (primary_muscle, difficulty, intent_type, is_active);

CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY idx_user_sessions_recent
ON workout_sessions (user_id, completed_at DESC)
WHERE status = 'COMPLETED';

CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY idx_share_cards_user_rarity
ON share_cards (user_id, rarity, created_at DESC);

CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY idx_equipment_frequency_date
ON equipment_frequencies (equipment_code, date DESC);
```

### API Response Time Targets

| API Endpoint | Target | Notes |
|--------------|--------|-------|
| Quick Recommendation | <5s | 复杂算法 |
| Card Generation | <800ms | 图像合成 |
| AI Recognition | <2s | TensorFlow 推理 |
| Supabase CRUD | <300ms | 自动 REST |
| Rarity Calculation | <500ms | 全局统计 |

---

## 📚 Error Handling

### Standard Error Format

```json
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "code": "VALIDATION_ERROR",
    "message": "Invalid equipment code",
    "details": {
      "field": "equipment",
      "value": "invalid_code"
    },
    "timestamp": "2024-10-30T10:30:00Z"
  }
}
```

### Common Error Codes

| Code | HTTP Status | Description |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `VALIDATION_ERROR` | 400 | 请求参数验证失败 |
| `UNAUTHORIZED` | 401 | JWT token 无效或过期 |
| `FORBIDDEN` | 403 | 无权访问该资源 |
| `NOT_FOUND` | 404 | 资源不存在 |
| `ALREADY_JOINED` | 409 | 已加入主题周 |
| `THEME_WEEK_ENDED` | 410 | 主题周已结束 |
| `RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED` | 429 | 请求频率超限 |
| `INTERNAL_ERROR` | 500 | 服务器内部错误 |

